msmod: Multispecies models

William K. Morris

2015-11-18

Fitting multispecies models

  • Multispecies trait models (MSTMs; see Pollock etal, 2012)
  • Joint Species Distribution Models (JSDMs; see Pollock etal, 2014)

The Grampians Eucalyptus dataset

Fitting a mutlispecies trait model

library(msmod)
msm_glmer <- 
  msm(y = "present", sites = "plot", x = "logit_rock", species = "species",
  traits = "ln_sla", data = eucs, type = "mstm", method = "glmer")

summary(msm_glmer)

Coefficient plot

coef_plot(msm_glmer)

Trait vs Environment plot

te_plot(msm_glmer, "logit_rock", "ln_sla")
